#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:1
msgid "E4087"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:3
msgid "Mutating something immutable, such as a variable or struct field."
msgstr "尝试修改不可变的对象，例如变量或结构体的字段。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:5
msgid ""
"MoonBit requires programmers to explicitly declare mutable variables and "
"struct fields. Notice that in MoonBit, variable mutability only refers to"
" the variable itself, not the value it holds. So when you declare an "
"immutable `let` value of type `Array[T]`, `Ref[T]`, or a `struct` with "
"mutable fields, you can still mutate the inner structure, but cannot "
"replace the value of the whole variable."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 要求程序员明确声明可变的变量和结构体字段。请注意，MoonBit "
"中变量的可变性仅指变量本身，而不是它持有的值。如果您声明了一个不可变的变量，但变量的类型是 `Array[T]`、`Ref[T]` 或有可变字段的"
" `struct`，您依然可以修改变量的内部结构，只是不能整个替换变量的值。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:12
msgid ""
"Tuples are always immutable. If you want mutability, use a `struct` with "
"mutable fields instead."
msgstr "元组永远是不可变的，如果想要可变性，应当使用有可变字段的 `struct`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:14
msgid "Erroneous Example"
msgstr "错误示例："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:16
msgid "Variable mutation:"
msgstr "变量修改："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:18
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let a = 0\n"
"  a = 1\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:22
msgid "Struct field mutation:"
msgstr "结构体字段修改："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:24
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct S {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let s = { x: 1 }\n"
"  println(s.x)\n"
"  s.x = 2\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:28
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:30
msgid ""
"To fix this error, you need to declare the variable as mutable by adding "
"the `mut` keyword before the variable name or struct field name."
msgstr "为了修复此错误，您需要将变量或结构体字段声明为可变的，方法是在变量名前添加 `mut` 关键字。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4087.md:33
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let mut a = 0\n"
"  a = 1\n"
"  println(a)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"priv struct S {\n"
"  mut x : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let s = { x: 1 }\n"
"  s.x = 2\n"
"  println(s.x)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

